        "title": "Adhan (Call to Prayer) & Responses",
        "body": "\n                    <p>The Adhan is the Islamic call to prayer. When hearing the Adhan, one should stop talking, listen attentively, and repeat what the Mu'adhin (caller) says, with a few specific exceptions.</p>\n                    \n                    <h4>Step-by-Step Adhan & Hearer's Response</h4>\n                    \n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 4 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Allahu Akbar (Allah is the Greatest)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> Allahu Akbar</p>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 2 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">أَشْهَدُ أَنْ لَا إِلٰهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ash-hadu an la ilaha illallah (I bear witness that there is no deity but Allah)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> Ash-hadu an la ilaha illallah</p>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 2 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">أَشْهَدُ أَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا رَسُولُ اللّٰهِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ash-hadu anna Muhammadan Rasulullah (I bear witness that Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> Ash-hadu anna Muhammadan Rasulullah</p>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 2 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">حَيَّ عَلَى الصَّلَاةِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Hayya 'alas-salah (Hasten to prayer)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> <em>La hawla wa la quwwata illa billah</em> (There is no might nor power except with Allah)</p>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 2 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">حَيَّ عَلَى الْفَلَاحِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Hayya 'alal-falah (Hasten to success)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> <em>La hawla wa la quwwata illa billah</em></p>\n\n                    <div style=\"background:var(--bg-secondary); padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px 0;\">\n                        <h5>* Special Addition for Fajr Prayer Only *</h5>\n                        <p>During the Fajr Adhan, after saying 'Hayya alal-falah', the Mu'adhin adds the following 2 times:</p>\n                        <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">اَلصَّلَاةُ خَيْرٌ مِنَ النَّوْمِ</div>\n                        <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 As-salatu khayrum-minan-nawm (Prayer is better than sleep)</div>\n                        <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> <em>Sadaqta wa bararta</em> (You have spoken the truth and done well)</p>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 2 Times</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">اللَّهُ أَكْبَرُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Allahu Akbar (Allah is the Greatest)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> Allahu Akbar</p>\n\n                    <p><strong>Caller (Mu'adhin): 1 Time</strong></p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">لَا إِلٰهَ إِلَّا اللّٰهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 La ilaha illallah (There is no deity but Allah)</div>\n                    <p><strong>You Reply:</strong> La ilaha illallah</p>\n\n                    <h4>Dua After Adhan</h4>\n                    <p>After the call has finished, it is highly recommended to recite the following Dua:</p>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">اللَّهُمَّ رَبَّ هَذِهِ الدَّعْوَةِ التَّامَّةِ، وَالصَّلَاةِ الْقَائِمَةِ، آتِ مُحَمَّدًا الْوَسِيلَةَ وَالْفَضِيلَةَ، وَابْعَثْهُ مَقَامًا مَحْمُودًا الَّذِي وَعَدْتَهُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Allahumma Rabba hadhihid-da'watit-tammah, was-salatil-qa'imah, ati Muhammadan al-wasilata wal-fadhilah, wab'ath-hu maqaman mahmudan alladhi wa'adtah.</div>\n                    <p>\"O Allah, Lord of this perfect call and established prayer. Grant Muhammad the intercession and favor, and raise him to the honored station You have promised him.\" (Sahih Bukhari 614)</p>\n                ",
