        "body": "\n                    <h4>Upon Waking Up</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَحْيَانَا بَعْدَ مَا أَمَاتَنَا وَإِلَيْهِ النُّشُورُ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Alhamdu lillahil-ladhi ahyana ba'da ma amatana wa ilayhin-nushur</div>\n                    <p>\"Praise is for Allah who gave us life after death, and unto Him is the resurrection.\" (Sahih Bukhari 6312)</p>\n                    <h4>Before Eating</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَعَلَى بَرَكَةِ اللَّهِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillahi wa 'ala barakatillah</div>\n                    <p>\"In the name of Allah and with His blessings.\" (Mustadrak Al-Hakim 7124)</p>\n                    <h4>After Eating</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">الْحَمْدُ لِلَّهِ الَّذِي أَطْعَمَنَا وَسَقَانَا وَجَعَلَنَا مُسْلِمِينَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Alhamdu lillahil-ladhi at'amana wa saqana wa ja'alana Muslimeen</div>\n                    <p>(Abu Dawud 3850)</p>\n                    <h4>When Leaving Home</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ تَوَكَّلْتُ عَلَى اللَّهِ وَلَا حَوْلَ وَلَا قُوَّةَ إِلَّا بِاللَّهِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillah, tawakkaltu 'alallah, wa la hawla wa la quwwata illa billah</div>\n                    <p>\"In the name of Allah, I trust in Allah. There is no might except with Allah.\" (Abu Dawud 5095)</p>\n                    <h4>When Entering Home</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ وَلَجْنَا وَبِسْمِ اللَّهِ خَرَجْنَا وَعَلَى اللَّهِ رَبِّنَا تَوَكَّلْنَا</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillahi walajna, wa bismillahi kharajna, wa 'alallahi Rabbina tawakkalna</div>\n                    <p>(Abu Dawud 5096)</p>\n                    <h4>Before Sleeping</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِاسْمِكَ اللَّهُمَّ أَمُوتُ وَأَحْيَا</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismika Allahumma amutu wa ahya</div>\n                    <p>\"In Your name, O Allah, I die and I live.\" (Sahih Bukhari 6312)</p>\n                    <h4>For Traveling</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">سُبْحَانَ الَّذِي سَخَّرَ لَنَا هَذَا وَمَا كُنَّا لَهُ مُقْرِنِينَ وَإِنَّا إِلَى رَبِّنَا لَمُنْقَلِبُونَ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Subhanal-ladhi sakhkhara lana hadha wa ma kunna lahu muqrinin. Wa inna ila Rabbina lamunqalibun.</div>\n                    <p>\"Glory to Him who subjected this to us. Unto our Lord we shall return.\" (Quran 43:13-14)</p>\n                    <h4>For Anxiety & Distress</h4>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">اللَّهُمَّ إِنِّي أَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْهَمِّ وَالْحُزْنِ وَأَعُوذُ بِكَ مِنَ الْعَجْزِ وَالْكَسَلِ</div>\n                    <div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Allahumma inni a'udhu bika minal-hammi wal-huzn, wa a'udhu bika minal-'ajzi wal-kasal</div>\n                    <p>\"O Allah, I seek refuge from worry, grief, inability, and laziness.\" (Sahih Bukhari 2893)</p>\n                ",
