        "body": "\n<p>Surah 114, seeking refuge in Allah from the evil within and whispers of jinn and men.</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">بِسْمِ اللَّهِ الرَّحْمَٰنِ الرَّحِيمِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Bismillahir-Rahmanir-Rahim</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">قُلْ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ النَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Qul a'oodhu birabbin-naas</div>\n<p>Say, \"I seek refuge in the Lord of mankind,</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">مَلِكِ النَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Malikin-naas</div>\n<p>The Sovereign of mankind,</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">إِلَٰهِ النَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Ilaahin-naas</div>\n<p>The God of mankind,</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">مِنْ شَرِّ الْوَسْوَاسِ الْخَنَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Min sharril-waswaasil-khannaas</div>\n<p>From the evil of the retreating whisperer -</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">الَّذِي يُوَسْوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ النَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Alladhee yuwaswisu fee sudoorin-naas</div>\n<p>Who whispers [evil] into the breasts of mankind -</p>\n<div class=\"tutorial-arabic\">مِنَ الْجِنَّةِ وَالنَّاسِ</div>\n<div class=\"tutorial-pronunciation\">🔊 Minal-jinnati wan-naas</div>\n<p>From among the jinn and mankind.\"</p>\n",
